  <name>Album</name>
  <summary>A photo and video album application for GNOME</summary>
	<description>
	  <p>A photo and video album application for GNOME.
      Built with GTK 4 and libadwaita, designed to be well
	    integrated with GNOME technologies and mobile devices.</p>
	  <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>View your photos and video library</li>
      <li>Create new Albums to organize memories</li>
      <li>Flip, rotate, and crop your photos</li>
      <li>Inspect rich metadata for photos</li>
    </ul>
	</description>
